1 NOTE English playwright, poet, and actor, widely regarded as the greatest
2 CONT writer in the English language. Author of approximately 39 plays
2 CONT including Hamlet, Macbeth, Romeo and Juliet, and A Midsummer Night's
2 CONT Dream, as well as 154 sonnets. He was a part-owner of the playing
2 CONT company the Lord Chamberlain's Men, later the King's Men.
