1 NOTE Father of William Shakespeare. A successful glove maker and alderman
2 CONT in Stratford-upon-Avon who held several municipal positions including
2 CONT High Bailiff, the town's highest elected office. He later faced
2 CONT financial difficulties and was stripped of his alderman status.
